116
00:11:04,983 --> 00:11:08,525
- Oh, hi.
- Hi, Gene. Hi.

117
00:11:08,608 --> 00:11:10,358
How's the dancin'?

118
00:11:10,442 --> 00:11:14,067
- Oh, good, yeah.
- Yeah?

119
00:11:14,192 --> 00:11:19,067
You want to come to me and Bill's
place and listen to some music?

120
00:11:19,192 --> 00:11:23,900
That... that would be lovely.
But we couldn't.

121
00:11:23,983 --> 00:11:26,900
- Come on. Come on.
- Yeah, I'll...

122
00:11:26,942 --> 00:11:29,025
Let's go. Come on.

123
00:11:37,317 --> 00:11:39,775
You should ask Bill about his money.

124
00:11:39,817 --> 00:11:42,858
Linda likes it
when we talk about that.

125
00:11:44,858 --> 00:11:47,358
You're doing a nice job of these.

126
