Oh, you always pay right on time.

147
00:14:23,817 --> 00:14:26,983
Don't worry about Gene,
I'll get him to school.

148
00:14:27,108 --> 00:14:29,317
Thank you. Thanks very much.

149
00:14:29,358 --> 00:14:31,358
Remember your bag.

150
00:14:32,525 --> 00:14:35,358
- Bye.
- Bye.

151
