153
00:14:41,150 --> 00:14:45,025
I don't think
inside you're serious at all.

154
00:14:45,067 --> 00:14:47,025
I don't know.

155
00:14:47,608 --> 00:14:49,733
- Not always.
- Cvalda.

156
00:14:49,817 --> 00:14:54,442
- Why do you call me that?
- It's like... someone who's...

157
00:14:55,608 --> 00:14:57,983
- What?
- Dunno, big and happy.

158
00:14:58,067 --> 00:15:01,983
Hey! I'm not that big.
Happy, I don't know.

159
00:15:02,025 --> 00:15:05,442
