- Please, be quiet.
- She doesn't see that well.

166
00:15:28,483 --> 00:15:32,483
- I paid good money to see this.
- So did she.

167
00:15:34,525 --> 00:15:36,483
I love it when they dance.

168
00:15:36,608 --> 00:15:39,525
It's a musical,
of course they're dancing!

169
00:15:39,608 --> 00:15:41,733
- We know.
- You're so smart!

170
00:15:41,775 --> 00:15:43,858
- Yes.
- Oh.

171
00:15:44,900 --> 00:15:46,942
I think you made friends, Kathy.

172
00:15:47,025 --> 00:15:48,400
Shh!

173
00:15:59,525 --> 00:16:00,942
So?

174
00:16:03,775 --> 00:16:06,067
So what did she say?

175
00:16:06,150 --> 00:16:08,150
- What?
- What did she say?

176
00:16:08,192 --> 00:16:10,233
She didn't say anything.

177
00:16:10,317 --> 00:16:13,025
Are you trying to tell me something?

178
00:16:13,108 --> 00:16:15,525
It's about the bike.

179
00:16:15,650 --> 00:16:18,567
- The bike?
- Mmm. The bike.

180
00:16:18,692 --> 00:16:22,650
Oh... I-I cannot give...
give Gene a bike.

181
00:16:22,775 --> 00:16:25,608
- Is this his idea?
- It is not.

182
00:16:25,733 --> 00:16:27,817
- Gene?
- Yeah?

183
00:16:27,900 --> 00:16:30,275
Did you ask them to come over?

184
00:16:30,358 --> 00:16:31,775
No.

185
00:16:31,858 --> 00:16:35,317
No, he doesn't
know anything, Selma. Frankly.

186
00:16:35,400 --> 00:16:38,317
- Why? Have I done something?
- No.

187
00:16:38,400 --> 00:16:40,358
I haven't got the money.

188
00:16:41,525 --> 00:16:45,150
I'm almost the only kid in class
who doesn't have a bike.

189
00:16:45,233 --> 00:16:48,067
I even know a boy
who's got a scooter.

190
00:16:48,192 --> 00:16:50,900
You all know I haven't got any money.

191
00:16:50,983 --> 00:16:53,192
All the extra money I've got...

192
00:16:53,233 --> 00:16:56,775
The times I save up -
I send it to Grandpa.

193
00:16:56,858 --> 00:17:00,567
Come and have a look.
Your mother is only teasing.

194
00:17:00,608 --> 00:17:02,692
Look what she's brought for you!

195
00:17:02,775 --> 00:17:04,108
It's a bike!

196
00:17:04,192 --> 00:17:07,108
- We can't accept that.
- It's not new.

197
00:17:07,233 --> 00:17:11,983
I can't give him any expensive things
- not even for his birthday.

198
00:17:12,067 --> 00:17:15,483
He's just gotta accept
I'm not that sort of mum.

199
00:17:15,525 --> 00:17:20,483
I- I-I'm just not
that kind of mother, G-Gene...

200
00:17:20,525 --> 00:17:23,775
Can't you be that kind of a mother?

201
00:17:23,858 --> 00:17:25,900
It's not exactly a scooter.

202
00:17:25,983 --> 00:17:28,400
We'll see.

203
00:17:30,067 --> 00:17:33,567
- Careful! Careful!
- Don't ride so fast!

204
00:17:35,442 --> 00:17:37,608
Gene, bring it over here.

205
00:17:41,275 --> 00:17:45,025
- He looks very happy.
- He does look happy.

206
00:17:45,108 --> 00:17:47,817
Here he comes again.
Attention!

207
00:17:47,942 --> 00:17:50,108
Bring it over here.

208
00:17:50,150 --> 00:17:53,025
- Mom?
- OK.

209
00:17:53,067 --> 00:17:55,192
Did you hear that?

210
00:17:55,275 --> 00:17:57,692
- Did you say OK?
- Yeah.

211
00:17:57,817 --> 00:18:00,733
- She said OK?
- Yeah.

212
00:18:00,817 --> 00:18:05,067
- But promise to go to school.
- Yes, yes.

213
00:18:05,150 --> 00:18:07,567
Every day... on time.

214
00:18:07,650 --> 00:18:10,775
I didn't know
you were such a good biker.

215
00:18:10,858 --> 00:18:13,150
Rust and women are the same.

216
00:18:13,233 --> 00:18:15,442
Rust and women are the same?

217
00:18:15,525 --> 00:18:17,358
Yeah, I'm just saying...

218
00:18:17,442 --> 00:18:20,067
- Your father said that.
- Yeah.

219
00:18:21,525 --> 00:18:23,650
I didn't know what it meant.

220
00:18:29,733 --> 00:18:32,358
He is so kind. Look at me...

221
00:18:32,442 --> 00:18:35,400
He did all the work.
He's really kind.

222
00:18:37,233 --> 00:18:39,400
Thank you, Jeff.

223
00:18:39,525 --> 00:18:40,983
You're welcome.

224
00:18:48,108 --> 00:18:49,858
Come in.

225
00:18:50,733 --> 00:18:52,483
Something up, Bill?

226
00:18:54,150 --> 00:18:56,567
No. I just couldn't sleep,
that's all.

227
00:19:03,775 --> 00:19:06,275
I have no money.

228
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:10,317
