It's gone.

229
00:19:14,775 --> 00:19:16,733
And Linda...

230
00:19:18,608 --> 00:19:20,567
Ah, Linda.

231
00:19:21,525 --> 00:19:23,483
She just spends and spends.

232
00:19:27,025 --> 00:19:29,775
And my salary is nowhere near enough.

233
00:19:30,942 --> 00:19:33,733
I can't say no to her.

234
00:19:33,817 --> 00:19:37,150
