I was looking for you.

410
00:33:32,317 --> 00:33:35,400
Just have to go to a drama rehearsal.

411
00:33:35,483 --> 00:33:37,733
What do you say?

412
00:33:37,775 --> 00:33:41,275
You always ride your bike.
You have it over there.

413
00:33:41,317 --> 00:33:45,608
