it would be quicker if I walk.

414
00:33:46,192 --> 00:33:48,025
How do you reckon that?

415
00:33:48,108 --> 00:33:51,525
I'd just walk along
the railroad tracks.

416
00:33:52,650 --> 00:33:55,775
It's, a... short cut.

417
00:34:14,442 --> 00:34:17,400
