00:46:25,775 --> 00:46:29,275
This is
Selma's entrance, OK? Yeah?

535
00:46:30,483 --> 00:46:32,108
OK, Paul, please.

536
00:46:32,150 --> 00:46:34,650
#.. an absurd little bird... #

537
00:46:34,733 --> 00:46:37,317
How far do you think it is?

538
00:46:37,358 --> 00:46:38,817
I don't know.

539
00:46:40,400 --> 00:46:44,108
# So long, farewell,
auf wiedersehen, goodbye... #

