652
00:55:56,942 --> 00:56:03,650
# Your grandson's hand
as he plays with your hair

653
00:56:03,685 --> 00:56:09,900
# To be honest, I really don't care

654
00:56:31,108 --> 00:56:34,275
# I've seen it all

655
00:56:34,317 --> 00:56:37,192
# I have seen the dark

656
00:56:37,317 --> 00:56:43,358
# I have seen the brightness
in one little spark

