I got today...

708
01:02:51,025 --> 01:02:53,025
which makes it...

709
01:02:54,192 --> 01:02:59,817
2,056... ten cents.

710
01:02:59,900 --> 01:03:01,858
It's not enough...

711
01:03:02,900 --> 01:03:04,858
but it'll have to do.

712
01:03:04,900 --> 01:03:06,983
- Selma.
- Bye, Bill.

713
01:03:07,067 --> 01:03:08,442
Selma.

714
01:03:15,108 --> 01:03:17,067
Selma, stop.

715
01:03:19,567 --> 01:03:22,108
I'm pointing my gun at you, Selma.

716
01:03:26,525 --> 01:03:28,608
I don't believe you.

717
01:03:28,692 --> 01:03:32,400
You're just trying to scare me.
I can't see a gun.

718
01:03:34,317 --> 01:03:38,608
Just feel this.
Feel this. Feel it. Feel it!

719
01:03:40,608 --> 01:03:43,150
Do you believe I have the gun?

720
01:03:43,275 --> 01:03:46,650
I believe you. But it's my money.

721
01:03:46,733 --> 01:03:50,817
No, it's my money.
It's the money I had in MY box

722
01:03:50,900 --> 01:03:53,400
and you're trying
to steal it from me.

723
01:03:53,483 --> 01:03:55,442
Selma! Selma!

724
01:03:55,525 --> 01:04:00,817
SELMA! STOP! SELMA, STOP!
LINDA! LINDA! LINDA!

725
01:04:00,900 --> 01:04:03,067
What's the matter, Bill?

726
01:04:04,067 --> 01:04:06,400
She was trying to steal our money.

727
01:04:08,025 --> 01:04:11,233
She knew I had the gun
in my drawer and she...

728
01:04:11,358 --> 01:04:13,942
Is that why you wanted him?
For the money?

729
01:04:13,977 --> 01:04:16,483
Run to the car and get my handcuffs.

730
01:04:16,608 --> 01:04:18,567
Go get the handcuffs.

731
01:04:20,275 --> 01:04:21,900
Give me the money.

732
01:04:30,025 --> 01:04:32,025
Where should I go?

733
01:04:37,900 --> 01:04:40,025
Gimme the money. Give me...

734
01:04:40,108 --> 01:04:43,442
No! No! No!

735
01:04:52,358 --> 01:04:54,358
You shot me.

736
01:04:57,150 --> 01:04:59,150
I'm gonna...

737
01:05:00,525 --> 01:05:03,525
No, no, Selma,
you did the right thing.

738
01:05:03,650 --> 01:05:06,150
I should have done it myself.

739
01:05:11,692 --> 01:05:13,692
Kill me.

740
01:05:15,942 --> 01:05:17,900
Just kill me.

741
01:05:19,442 --> 01:05:24,817
Be my friend and show some
mercy, please, and just kill me.

742
01:05:25,650 --> 01:05:27,608
You handcuffs aren't in the car.

743
01:05:27,733 --> 01:05:30,317
Show some mercy, Selma, and just...

744
01:05:35,108 --> 01:05:37,775
Linda, run. Run up to Miller's farm.

745
01:05:37,858 --> 01:05:41,025
Call the station
and tell them to hurry.

746
01:05:41,067 --> 01:05:43,733
RUN! GET UP THERE!
Go to Miller's farm!

747
01:05:47,067 --> 01:05:49,025
If you want the money...

748
01:05:53,775 --> 01:05:56,025
You're going to have to kill me.

749
01:05:56,108 --> 01:05:58,317
Don't do this to me.

750
01:06:08,275 --> 01:06:10,483
Don't do this to me.

751
01:06:12,025 --> 01:06:13,942
I'm not letting go.

752
01:06:15,567 --> 01:06:16,942
No.

753
01:06:18,525 --> 01:06:24,025
Just shoot me. Just shoot me.
Shoot me! Shoot me! Shoot me!

754
01:06:37,858 --> 01:06:42,150
Can't you just stand up
and pull the goddamn trigger!

755
01:07:02,400 --> 01:07:04,775
I want to take my money.

